title: No. 2 Baylor rolls over WVU 62-38, Coleman has 3 TD catches
text:
> Texas No. 2 Baylor rolls over WVU 62-38, Coleman has 3 TD catches Baylor wide receiver Corey Coleman (1) scores past West Virginia defensive lineman Eric Kinsey (45) in the second half of an NCAA college football game, Saturday, Oct 17, 2015, in Waco, Texas. Baylor won 62-38. (AP Photo/Rod Aydelotte)
